Ing '''balubad''' (''Anacardium occidentale''; [[syn.]] ''Anacardium curatellifolium'' [[A.St.-Hil.]]) metung yang [[pun]] kareng [[mamulaklak a tanaman]] family [[Anacardiaceae]]. Ing [[tanaman]] Katutubu ya king pangulungaslagang [[Brazil]], nung nu mayayaus ya keng [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] a lagyu a ''Caju'' (ing bunga) o ''Cajueiro'' (ing pun).
Ngeni daragul ya kareng lugal a [[tropics|tropical]] [[klima]] para keng kayang balubad a mani.


